oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Framed photograph of Confederate veterans from Lawrence County
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This framed photograph of nine Confederate veterans from Lawrence County was taken in the late 1800s or early 1900s. It includes Polk Grimes (top row, last on the right) and John McCaleb (botton row, 2nd from the left). It was taken in the late 1800s or early 1900s.
